    title: "AI Agents vs Chatbots: What's the Real Difference in",
    excerpt: "Most businesses think they need a chatbot. What they actually need is an AI agent.",
    category: "AI Solutions",
    date: "July 5, 2026",
    readTime: "11 min read",
